video.title: FETCH! with Ruff Ruffman
video.synopsis: Ruff Ruffman is the canine host of this partly animated reality show in which kids attempt to meet wacky challenges involving science.

episodes.synopsis: Two FETCHers track skunks and use chemistry to neutralize skunk spray, while two others learn to "brave the waves" and become junior lifeguards.
episodes.title: The Debut of Smell-o-Vision

episodes.synopsis: Noel and Jay learn about buildings to construct a tower out of cards. Sam and Sammy create a public service announcement about rescuing animals.
episodes.title: When Home Is a House of Cards

episodes.synopsis: DJ, Jay and Sam meet with a chemistry expert to learn how to fight stains, and Ruff sends Noel to a fire academy so she can learn how to fight fires.
episodes.title: Just Call Him 'Spot'

episodes.synopsis: Ruff sends Sam to a meeting with Sen. Ted Kennedy while Noel, Sammy and DJ are challenged to design a float for Ruff's political campaign!
episodes.title: Mr. Ruffman Goes to Washington

episodes.synopsis: To impress Charlene's mom, Ruff sends Harsha, DJ and Sam to construct a gift. Also, Jay visits a cosmetologist to learn how to cut hair and do makeup.
episodes.title: How Not to Impress a Poodle's Mother

episodes.synopsis: Ruff sends Harsha, Noel and Sam to build a structure that can protect a tortilla chip and Grandma Ruffman's cake. Sammy visits Spanish Harlem.
episodes.title: There's Food Safety and Then There's Food Safety

episodes.synopsis: Ruff asks Sammy and DJ to learn how to square dance. Meanwhile, Harsha and Jay go to the zoo to find out what kinds of habitats make animals happy.
episodes.title: Do-Se-Dos and Do-Se-Don'ts

episodes.synopsis: Uncle MacRuffmantosh has informed Ruff and the FETCHers that a secret order of cats has been hiding the secret behind the Mona Lisa's smile for years.
episodes.title: The DogVinci Code

episodes.synopsis: Noel, Sammy and Jay are dispatched to Thompson Island, where they learn about insects, while Harsha learns about powwows in New Mexico.
episodes.title: What's Bugging Ruff

episodes.synopsis: DJ and Sammy meet with an athletic shoe designer to see if they can design a better shoe for Ruff. Jay and Sam learn crowd-gathering techniques.
episodes.title: Will They Like the Show? It's a Shoe-in!

episodes.synopsis: Sam and Sammy work on helping Ruff decrease his electricity consumption, while Harsha and Noel get singing lessons and have to perform ... live!
episodes.title: Socket to Me

episodes.synopsis: Ruff's nephew uses the FETCHers as pawns in his live-action role-playing game. They go to Wing's Castle dressed as elves, wizards and dwarves.
episodes.title: Dog of the Rings

episodes.synopsis: Uncle MacRuffmantosh tells Ruff about their pirate ancestor, whose treasure remains at the bottom of the sea. Ruff sends Sammy and Jay to retrieve it.
episodes.title: Arrgh -- All Me Eggs Are Cracked!

episodes.synopsis: Noel and DJ meet a bunch of border collies to help command a herd of sheep. Harsha and Sam find out how animals there survive in the desert.
episodes.title: Feeling Sheepish, Ruff?

episodes.synopsis: Ruff sends DJ to a dog obedience school to become an expert trainer, while Noel, Sammy and Jay go to an engineering school to design a home for Chet.
episodes.title: I'll Ruff and I'll Ruff and I'll Blow Your House Down

episodes.synopsis: Grandma is accused of trying to break Ruff's twin, Scruff, out of prison! The FETCHers try the case with help from real lawyers in a real courtroom.
episodes.title: The People vs. Grandma Ruffman

episodes.synopsis: Harsha and Sammy become radio reporters and conduct a news report on Brian Freeze, while Noel and DJ invent a new Ruff Ruffman toy.
episodes.title: Just Toying with Ruff

episodes.synopsis: Ruff sends Harsha and DJ out to engineer a "puck stopper" that he can use as goalie in a hockey game. Meanwhile, Jay and Noel trade places for a day.
episodes.title: The Ol' Switcheroo

episodes.synopsis: Ruff's twin brother, Scruff, devises a series of elimination games that take place in a variety of Ruff and Scruff's important childhood haunts.
episodes.title: Finale

episodes.synopsis: When show host Ruff is fired by his dog-hating boss, he takes an epic cartoon journey to Australia to get his job back.
episodes.title: Season Four Is Canceled

episodes.synopsis: To help Ruff find a family heirloom, contestants must pole-vault over a fence, while others learn the sport of fencing.
episodes.title: Don't Like Fencing? Try Fencing!

episodes.synopsis: Ruff Meals need less packaging and more sales: Three FETCHers learn how to make them eco-friendly, while Bethany learns to conduct music for a jingle.
episodes.title: The RuffMeal Needs More Roughage

episodes.synopsis: Blossom says pigs are smarter than dogs, so Ruff sends the kids out to prove she's wrong, and to learn how smart Shamu the killer whale is.
episodes.title: Ruff Pigs Out and Has a Whale of a Time

episodes.synopsis: Handcuffed to Ruff, Blossom organizes her own FETCH! challenge: a 50-mile race in which the winning team must emit the least amount of carbon dioxide.
episodes.title: Ruff's Just Fueling Around

episodes.synopsis: Ruff's fear of arachnids and ballet inspires new challenges: Two kids must work in a spider lab while Brian becomes a ballet dancer.
episodes.title: Finding Eight-Legged Tights Isn't Easy

episodes.synopsis: Ruff wants to prove he'll be able to rock out on stage with his musician cousin's band, so Sterling and Liza are sent to a rock 'n' roll band camp.
episodes.title: Ruff Rocks the (Environmentally Sustainable) House!

episodes.synopsis: Ruff's urgent need for a doggy potty break sends Bethany and Isaac to NASA, where they learn how astronauts deal with waste in space.
episodes.title: Doggie Duties

episodes.synopsis: A new beauty cream turns Ruff into a turkey vulture, so all the FETCHers must learn about this odd bird and use advertising to improve its image.
episodes.title: How Not to Impress the Press

episodes.synopsis: Ruff's discomfort around his penguin colleagues leads the kids to get aquatic bird tips from the New England Aquarium and learn about improvisation.
episodes.title: How to Break the Ice and Also Waddle On It

episodes.synopsis: Ruff's new sport "Ruffball" is so boring that Talia and Liza meet up with a physics teacher to spark new ideas for perking up the game.
episodes.title: Blossom Bawls While Ruff Has a Ball With Balls

episodes.synopsis: While Talia and Isaac help pressured Ruff determine the smartest dog breed, Sterling and Brian learn about pressure by playing wheelchair basketball.
episodes.title: Ruff Bounces Back

episodes.synopsis: Nephew Glen turns Ruff and the kids into masked superheroes to battle "Gamma Ray Person," a villain harnessing the electromagnetic spectrum for evil.
episodes.title: Is it a Bird? Is it a Plane? It's Ruffmanman!

episodes.synopsis: Ruff's new business venture (a crustacean letter-delivery service) sends the FETCH! crew out to work on a shrimp boat and drive race cars.
episodes.title: Shrimp a la Cart

episodes.synopsis: When Ruff hears a phantom voice telling him to bake cookies, the FETCH teams scramble to learn how hearing works and to take cookie baking lessons.
episodes.title: Ruff Needs His Herring Checked

episodes.synopsis: To foil flower shop thief Le Purr, Brian patrols local florists while Talia and Sterling learn about laser lights, optics and security systems.
episodes.title: LePurr Strikes

episodes.synopsis: Ruff's poor bargain hunting skills send the FETCHers to the world's biggest flea market, and then to a sporting goods company for a new tennis racket.
episodes.title: Ruff's Yard Sale Makes a Racket

episodes.synopsis: To defeat cat-grooming shows in TV ratings, the FETCHers learn to groom goats and pick a better bike for Ruff to ride uphill to the Helmet of Victory.
episodes.title: Gearing Up For Getting Ruff's Goat

episodes.synopsis: The Helmet of Victory is only a train ride away. Can the FETCH crew solve railroad riddles that will unlock a mysterious briefcase?
episodes.title: How to Really Train Your Dog

episodes.synopsis: With The Helmet of Victory within arms' reach Ruff creates a final FETCH! Grand Champion challenge: Find and retrieve his family's magical heirloom.
episodes.title: Fetch Finale IV: The Prophecy Fulfilled!
